item.title: Mopar vet? what is it?
item.dc:creator: @si_force Si Force
item.description:
@si_force wrote:

It’s a myth, that’s all it is. Madness, absolute madness.

Really though, it’s a private group of members who are the ‘elite’ of the forum so to speak. To gain entry, you must be nominated and receive a ratio of 2:1+1 votes.

@common knowledge It was common knowledge a year or two ago, when it was a primary rank and a vet received a colour on the online list. However, this was changed a while ago and now the rank is invisible.
